Detailed Description

Test code for Symmetric Cipher support in FSL SHW API.

This file contains vectors and code to test fsl_shw_symmetric_encrypt(), fsl_shw_symmetric_decrypt(), and the functions associated with the Secret Key and Symmetric Context Objects.
